  "subject": "Fix docker tag based on CIMAN-132",
  "commit_message": "Fix docker tag based on CIMAN-132\n\nAlso specify the tox version.  If using the newest, 3.0.0,\ntox will fail due to not able to find pip.req.  So try the\nversion of tox used by the last successful tox run, 2.9.1.\nAlso fixing pip version to 9.0.3.\n\nIssue-ID: DCAEGEN2-206\nChange-Id: Iee6b635dc4fbe7e2b81d512627d7afd4097de635\nSigned-off-by: Lusheng Ji <lji@research.att.com>\n",
